'''HD 49798'''是在[[船尾座|船尾座]]的一顆[[聯星|聯星]]，距離地球大約650[[秒差距|秒差距]]。它的[[視星等|視星等]]為 +8.3等。

HD 49798是在1964年被發現是一顆罕見的，欠缺氫融合的[[O型次矮星|O型次矮星]]<ref name=jaschek>{{cite journal|bibcode=1963PASP...75..365J|title=HD 49798, a New O-Type Subdwarf|journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific|volume=75|pages=365|author1=Jaschek|first1=Mercedes|last2=Jaschek|first2=Carlos|year=1963|doi=10.1086/127968}}</ref>。它被認定是聯星，但是始終未能目視或從光譜檢測出其伴星<ref>{{cite journal|bibcode=1970MNRAS.150..215T|title=The spectroscopic orbit of the O-type subdwarf HD 49798|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_monthly-notices-of-the-royal-astronomical-society_1970_150_2/page/215|journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society|volume=150|issue=2|pages=215|author1=Thackeray|first1=A. D.|year=1970|doi=10.1093/mnras/150.2.215}}</ref>。
  
在它的附近，科學家發現了X射線源，並標示為RX J0648.0-4418。但是只有[[XMM-牛頓衛星|XMM-牛頓衛星]]太空望遠鏡能夠識別發出這個輻射的天體。它是一顆質量約為1.3[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]白矮星，在軌道上以13秒的週期環繞著HD 49798<ref>{{cite journal|bibcode=1997A&A...317..815B|title=The nature of the bright subdwarf HD 49798 and its X-ray pulsating companion|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomy-and-astrophysics_1997-01_317_3/page/815|journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics|volume=317|pages=815|author1=Bisscheroux|first1=B. C.|last2=Pols|first2=O. R.|last3=Kahabka|first3=P.|last4=Belloni|first4=T.|last5=Van Den Heuvel|first5=E. P. J.|year=1997}}</ref>。這一系統被認為是[[超新星|超新星]]的候選者，在數千年後可能爆炸成為[[Ia型超新星|Ia型超新星]] <ref>{{cite journal|bibcode=2012NewAR..56..122W|arxiv=1204.1155|title=Progenitors of type Ia supernovae|journal=New Astronomy Reviews|volume=56|issue=4|pages=122|author1=Wang|first1=Bo|last2=Han|first2=Zhanwen|year=2012|doi=10.1016/j.newar.2012.04.001}}</ref><ref name=liu>{{cite journal|bibcode=2015RAA....15.1813L|arxiv=1504.01461|title=Is the X-ray pulsating companion of HD 49798 a possible type Ia supernova progenitor?|journal=Research in Astronomy and Astrophysics|volume=15|issue=11|pages=1813|author1=Liu|first1=Dong-Dong|last2=Zhou|first2=Wei-Hong|last3=Wu|first3=Cheng-Yuan|last4=Wang|first4=Bo|year=2015|doi=10.1088/1674-4527/15/11/004}}</ref>。

